channel.title: What is the difference between
channel.description:
On a 317 DELTA, what is the difference between
[code=java] public static int Helm[] = {}; [/code]
[code=java] public static int fullHelm[] = {}; [/code]
[code=java] public static int fullMask[] = {}; [/code] ?
I know this is probably a dumb question but I want to know because I'm redoing my whole entire item.java and don't want to mess the helms and masks up.
Thanks, Sibor

what parts of the face covers.

fullMask only covers the front.
fullHelm covers everything.
Helm generally covers all but the face [Think Dragon med helm]
Normally, I put (for instance a dragon full helm) in Helm and fullHelm.
